Olive Sturgess https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Olive_Sturgess 0 Olive Dora Sturgess (born October 8, 1933) is a Canadian former actress of American television and three films. Though most of her appearances were in westerns, her longest-running role was as the model Carol Henning in 12 of the 155 episodes of NBC's situation comedy The Bob Cummings Show, which aired between 1956 and 1959.
